-----Odysync-Rozrost----


---> requirement

Unison - sudo apt-get install unison
pyinotify - sudo apt-get install python-pyinotify
ssh -  sudo apt-get -y install openssh-server ssh nano

---> use
sudo bash setup.sh

python init.py -dir <src> -config <config-file>

example:
python init.py -dir /home/saket/source/ -config sync.cfg

---> req files

sync.cfg file contains list to directories to be synced.
sample content for sync.cfg

[sync.dirs]
dir1: /home/saket/destination/1/
dir2: /home/saket/destination/2/
dir3: /home/saket/destination/3/
